e; max-width: 100%;"><div style="box-sizing: border-box; width: 1160px; display: flex;"><div data-id="b12e115" data-element_type="column" style="box-sizing: border-box; position: relative; min-height: 1px; display: flex; width: 1160px;"><div style="box-sizing: border-box; width: 1160px; position: relative; display: flex; padding: 0px 10px 10px;"><div style="box-sizing: border-box; position: relative; width: 1140px; flex-wrap: wrap; align-content: flex-start; display: flex;"><div data-id="7c752be" data-element_type="widget" data-widget_type="text-editor.default" style="box-sizing: border-box; position: relative; color: rgb(122, 122, 122); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-weight: 400; width: 1140px;"><div style="box-sizing: border-box; transition: background 0.3s ease 0s, border 0.3s ease 0s, border-radius 0.3s ease 0s, box-shadow 0.3s ease 0s, -webkit-border-radius 0.3s ease 0s, -webkit-box-shadow 0.3s ease 0s;"><div style="box-sizing: border-box;"><h3 style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 15px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0) !important; font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif; font-weight: 400; font-size: 20px; clear: both; text-align: justify;">&nbsp;</h3>
                                                                <h3 style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 15px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0) !important; font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif; font-weight: 400; font-size: 20px; clear: both; text-align: justify;">Bugungi kunda milliy iqtisodiyotni harakatlantiruvchi eng muhim omillardan biri bu mehnat va hayotiy qadriyatlarni muvaffaqiyatli ravishda uyg&lsquo;unlashtirishdir. O&lsquo;tgan asrda taniqli iqtisodchi Jon Meynard Keyns kelajakda avtomatlashtirish, yangi texnologiyalarga o&lsquo;tish va mehnat unumdorligini oshirish orqali odamlar haftasiga atigi 15 soat ishlaydi, deb bashorat qilgandi.</h3><h3 style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 15px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0) !important; font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif; font-weight: 400; font-size: 20px; clear: both; text-align: justify;">Yevropa davlatlari dunyoda ish vaqtini qisqartirish bo&lsquo;yicha yetakchi hisoblanadi.&nbsp;<strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">IHTT maʼlumotlariga</strong> ko&lsquo;ra, Yevropa mamlakatlarida o&lsquo;rtacha&nbsp;<strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">ish haftasi 37 soatni</strong> tashkil qiladi. Eng qisqa ish haftasi&nbsp;<strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">Norvegiya</strong> (33,5),&nbsp;<strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">Daniya</strong> (32,5) va&nbsp;<strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">Niderlandiya</strong> (29,4) kabi mamlakatlarda kuzatiladi. Bugungi kunda dunyoda o&lsquo;rtacha ish haftasi&nbsp;<strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">40 soatni</strong> tashkil qiladi. Biroq, so&lsquo;nggi o&lsquo;n yil ichida ish beruvchilar tomonidan dunyo bo&lsquo;ylab xodimlar uchun to&lsquo;liqsiz ish kuni va moslashuvchan ish jadvalini joriy etish tobora ommalashmoqda. Bandlikning ushbu usulidan ayniqsa, koronavirus pandemiyasi davrida keng foydalanildi.</h3><h3 style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 15px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0) !important; font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif; font-weight: 400; font-size: 20px; clear: both; text-align: justify;">Shuningdek, aholisi dunyoning qolgan qismiga qaraganda ko&lsquo;proq ishlaydigan davlatlar ham yo&lsquo;q emas.&nbsp;<strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">Kolumbiya&nbsp;</strong>(haftasiga 47,6 soat),&nbsp;<strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">Turkiya</strong> (46,4),&nbsp;<strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">Meksika</strong> (44,9) va&nbsp;<strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">Kosta-Rika</strong> (43,6) shunday mamlaktalar sirasiga kiradi. Tadqiqotlar ish kunining hozirgi sakkiz soat va undan ortiq meʼyori ishlaydigan odamning nafaqat sog&lsquo;ligi, balki mehnat unumdorligiga ham taʼsir qilishini ko&lsquo;rsatdi. &nbsp;Masalan, qo&lsquo;shimcha ish vaqti sezilarli darajada yuqori bo&lsquo;lgan&nbsp;<strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">Yaponiyada</strong> ish joyida hayotdan ko&lsquo;z yumish bilan bog&lsquo;liq holatlar ancha keng tarqalgan hodisaga aylandi. Ular hatto buning uchun atama ham o&lsquo;ylab topgan&nbsp;<strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">- karosi</strong>.<a href="https://imrs.uz/publications/articles-and-abstracts/four_day#_ftn1" name="_ftnref1" style="box-sizing: border-box; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-decoration: none; box-shadow: none;">[1]</a></h3><table style="box-sizing: border-box; border-collapse: collapse; border-spacing: 0px; margin: 0px 0px 1.5em; width: 1140px;"><tbody style="box-sizing: border-box;"><tr style="box-sizing: border-box;"><td style="box-sizing: border-box; padding: 5px; border: 1px solid rgb(221, 221, 221);"><h3 style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 15px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0) !important; font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif; font-weight: 400; font-size: 20px; clear: both; text-align: justify;"><em style="box-sizing: border-box; font-style: italic;">Maʼlumot uchun: Jahon sog&lsquo;liqni saqlash tashkilotining Xalqaro mehnat tashkiloti bilan birgalikda hisob-kitoblariga ko&lsquo;ra, 2016-yilda dunyoda qariyb 400 ming kishi haftasiga 55 soat va undan ortiq ishlashi oqibatida insultdan, 350 ming kishi yurak-qon tomir kasalliklaridan vafot etgan. 2000-2016 yillarda uzoq davom etgan mehnat tufayli kelib chiqqan yurak-qon tomir kasalliklaridan vafot etganlar soni 42 foizga, insultdan vafot etganlar soni esa 19 foizga oshgan</em><em style="box-sizing: border-box; font-style: italic;">1.</em></h3></td></tr></tbody></table><h3 style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 15px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0) !important; font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif; font-weight: 400; font-size: 20px; clear: both; text-align: justify;">Ish kunini qisqartirish g&lsquo;oyasi&nbsp;<strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">XXI asr</strong> boshidan beri ko&lsquo;plab mamlakatlarda muhokama qilinmoqda va sinovdan o&lsquo;tkazilayapti.&nbsp;<strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">2016-yilda Islandiyada</strong> bir necha kompaniyada xodimlarning ish haftasi 4-5 soatga qisqardi &ndash; biroq unumdorlik bir xil darajada saqlanib qoldi. Bundan tashqari, xodimlarning ishdan qoniqish darajasi oshdi, sog&lsquo;lig&lsquo;i sababli mehnatga layoqatsizlik kunlari kamaydi va umumiy farovonlik darajasi oshdi<a href="https://imrs.uz/publications/articles-and-abstracts/four_day#_ftn2" name="_ftnref2" style="box-sizing: border-box; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-decoration: none; box-shadow: none;">[2]</a>.</h3><h3 style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 15px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0) !important; font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif; font-weight: 400; font-size: 20px; clear: both; text-align: justify;"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">2018-yilda Perpetual Guardian&nbsp;</strong>(Yangi Zelandiya) birinchilardan bo&lsquo;lib tajriba o&lsquo;tkazdi va to&lsquo;liq ish haqini saqlab qolgan holda ish haftasini 4 kungacha qisqartirdi. Ushbu tajriba&nbsp;<strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">Oklend</strong> texnologiya universiteti olimlari tomonidan nazorat qilindi. Tadqiqot natijalari kompaniyada mehnat unumdorligi&nbsp;<strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">20 foizga oshgani</strong>, xodimlarning stress darajasi&nbsp;<strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">45 foizdan 38 foizga&nbsp;</strong>kamaygani, ish va shaxsiy hayot o&lsquo;rtasidagi muvozanat&nbsp;<strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">54 foizdan 78 foizga</strong> yaxshilanganini ko&lsquo;rsatdi<a href="https://imrs.uz/publications/articles-and-abstracts/four_day#_ftn3" name="_ftnref3" style="box-sizing: border-box; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-decoration: none; box-shadow: none;">[3]</a>.</h3><h3 style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 15px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0) !important; font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif; font-weight: 400; font-size: 20px; clear: both; text-align: justify;">Shvetsiyaning&nbsp;<strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">Gyoteborg&nbsp;</strong>munitsipalitetida ikki yildan ortiq vaqt davomida bir nechta kompaniya ish haqini kamaytirmasdan, 6 soatlik ish kunini qo&lsquo;lladi. Tajriba muvaffaqiyatli o&lsquo;tdi va shaharda&nbsp;<strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">17 nafar hamshira</strong> uchun qo&lsquo;shimcha ish o&lsquo;rni yaratildi. Bu esa kasallik varaqasi bo&lsquo;yicha xarajatlarni qisqartirish va mehnat madaniyati haqida global munozarani qo&lsquo;zg&lsquo;atdi, biroq bu yondashuvni butun munitsipalitetda qo&lsquo;llash juda qimmatga tushdi<a href="https://imrs.uz/publications/articles-and-abstracts/four_day#_ftn4" name="_ftnref4" style="box-sizing: border-box; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-decoration: none; box-shadow: none;">[4]</a>.</h3><h3 style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 15px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0) !important; font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif; font-weight: 400; font-size: 20px; clear: both; text-align: justify;">Bunday tajribalar juda ko&lsquo;plab mamlakatlarda o&lsquo;tkazib kelinmoqda. Samaradorlik yuqori bo&lsquo;lishiga qaramasdan, aksariyat davlatlar va kompaniyalar 4 kunlik ish haftasiga to&lsquo;liq o&lsquo;tishni rad etayapti. Buning asosiy sababi &ndash; katta xarajatlardir. Chunki yangi tizimga o&lsquo;tish davrida maoshlar bir xil darajada qolishi talab etiladi.</h3><h3 style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 15px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0) !important; font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif; font-weight: 400; font-size: 20px; clear: both; text-align: justify;">Rossiyalik ekspertlarning fikricha, Rossiyada to&lsquo;rt kunlik ish haftasiga o&lsquo;tish halokatli oqibatlarga olib kelishi mumkin. &quot;Agar ish haqi bir vaqtning o&lsquo;zida pasaymasa, bu ish kuchining&nbsp;<strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">20 foizga</strong> qimmatlashishiga olib keladi. Bu esa mehnat bozorida ham, umuman iqtisodiyotda ham keng ko&lsquo;lamdagi halokatli oqibatlarga olib kelishi mumkin va ayniqsa ishsizlik darajasi oshishiga sabab bo&lsquo;ladi. Agar ish haqi kamaysa, bu aholining qashshoqlashishiga, turmush darajasi va yalpi ichki mahsulotning keskin pasayishiga olib keladi. Ish kunlarini qisqartirish tashabbusi &ldquo;bosh og&lsquo;rig&lsquo;i&rdquo; va &ldquo;haqiqatga umuman to&lsquo;g&lsquo;ri kelmaydigan g&lsquo;oya&rdquo;- deydi Kapelyushnikov<a href="https://imrs.uz/publications/articles-and-abstracts/four_day#_ftn5" name="_ftnref5" style="box-sizing: border-box; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-decoration: none; box-shadow: none;">[5]</a>.</h3><h3 style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 15px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0) !important; font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif; font-weight: 400; font-size: 20px; clear: both; text-align: justify;"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">PMTI ekspertlari</strong> dunyoning turli mamlakatlarida bir ishchiga to&lsquo;g&lsquo;ri keladigan o&lsquo;rtacha yillik ish vaqti va bir soatlik ish vaqtiga to&lsquo;g&lsquo;ri keladigan YAIM o&lsquo;rtasidagi bog&lsquo;liqlikni aniqlash uchun tahlil o&lsquo;tkazdi. Maʼlumotlar bazasiga odamlar haftasiga&nbsp;<strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">32 soatdan ortiq ishlamaydigan&nbsp;</strong>va&nbsp;<strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">40 soatdan ortiq</strong> ishlaydigan davlatlar (Kolumbiya, Turkiya, Meksika) kiritildi.</h3><h3 style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 15px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0) !important; font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif; font-weight: 400; font-size: 20px; clear: both; text-align: justify;">Korrelyatsion tahlil natijalari shuni ko&lsquo;rsatdiki, bir soatlik ish vaqtiga to&lsquo;g&lsquo;ri keladigan YAIM hamda haftalik ish soatlari (0,027) o&lsquo;rtasida hech qanday bog&lsquo;liqlik yo&lsquo;q. Ushbu ko&lsquo;rsatkich odamlar haftasiga 35 soat yoki undan kam ishlaydigan mamlakatlarda ham, haftasiga 40 soat yoki undan ko&lsquo;proq ishlaydigan mamlakatlarda ham o&lsquo;zaro bog&lsquo;liq emas.</h3><h3 style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 15px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0) !important; font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif; font-weight: 400; font-size: 20px; clear: both; text-align: justify;">Shunday qilib, ish haftasining davomiyligi mehnat unumdorligiga sezilarli taʼsir ko&lsquo;rsatmaydi. O&lsquo;z navbatida, mehnat unumdorligini oshirish boshqa ko&lsquo;plab omillar (bajarilgan ish sifati, xodimlarning malakasi, xodimlarning ruhiy holati va boshqalar) kombinatsiyasiga bog&lsquo;liq.</h3></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></section></div></div></div></div></div>
        <header style="box-sizing: inherit; display: block; color: rgb(114, 114, 114); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;" id="isPasted"><h3 style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 15px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0) !important; font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif; font-weight: 400; font-size: 20px; clear: both; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; text-align: right;" id="isPasted">1-rasm</h3><h3 style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 15px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0) !important; font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif; font-weight: 400; font-size: 20px; clear: both; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; text-align: center;"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">Yillik ish soatlari va bir soatlik ish vaqtiga to&lsquo;g&lsquo;ri keladigan YAIM o&lsquo;rtasidagi<br style="box-sizing: border-box;">bog&lsquo;liqlikning tarqoq diagrammasi</strong></h3><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 15px; color: rgb(114, 114, 114); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; text-align: center;"><img data-fr-image-pasted="true" src="https://imrs.uz/public/ckfinder/userfiles/files/image(229).png" style="margin-left: 27%;box-sizing: border-box; border: none; height: 314px; max-width: 100%; border-radius: 0px; box-shadow: none; width: 624px;" class="fr-fic fr-dii"></p><h3 style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 15px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0) !important; font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif; font-weight: 400; font-size: 20px; clear: both; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; text-align: justify;">Dunyoning ko&lsquo;plab davlatlari ish haftasini qisqartirishni samarali yo&lsquo;llar bilan sinab ko&lsquo;rayotgan bir paytda, O&lsquo;zbekiston aholisi meʼyordagidan ko&lsquo;proq ishlamoqda. Bu holat fuqarolarning dam olish va hordiq chiqarish huquqi, shu jumladan ish kuni va haq to&lsquo;lanadigan taʼtillarni samarali cheklash bo&lsquo;yicha ijtimoiy huquqlari kafolatlarini qonun bilan mustahkamlashga oid &nbsp;masalalarni hal qilishni taqozo etadi. Shunday qilib, O&lsquo;zbekiston Respublikasi Konstitutsiyasining 38-moddasiga tegishli o&lsquo;zgartirishlar kiritilishi jamiyatning qulay mehnat sharoitlari hamda mehnatga layoqatliligini tiklashga bo&lsquo;lgan huquqlari asosiga aylanadi.</h3><h3 style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 15px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0) !important; font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif; font-weight: 400; font-size: 20px; clear: both; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; text-align: justify;"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">O&lsquo;zbekistonliklar ham Yevropa davlatlari aholisi kabi haftada 4 kun ishlasa nima bo&lsquo;ladi?</strong></h3><h3 style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 15px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0) !important; font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif; font-weight: 400; font-size: 20px; clear: both; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; text-align: justify;">O&lsquo;zbekistonning Yevropa amaliyotidagidek 4 kunlik ish haftasiga o&lsquo;tishi qanday oqibatlarga olib kelishi mumkin? Ushbu masalani ilmiy nuqtai nazardan ko&lsquo;rib chiqish maqsadga muvofiq. Buning uchun, birinchi navbatda, ish haftasining qisqarishi mehnat unumdorligiga qanday taʼsir qilishi mumkinligini tahlil qilish zarur.</h3><h3 style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 15px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0) !important; font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif; font-weight: 400; font-size: 20px; clear: both; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; text-align: justify;">O&lsquo;zbekistonda 4 kunlik ish haftasining mehnat unumdorligiga taʼsirini tahlil qilish uchun&nbsp;<strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">PMTI mutaxassislari</strong> respublika bo&lsquo;yicha mehnat unumdorligi va bir soatlik ish vaqtidagi mehnat unumdorligini hisoblab chiqdi.</h3><h3 style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 15px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0) !important; font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif; font-weight: 400; font-size: 20px; clear: both; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; text-align: justify;">Korrelyatsion tahlil natijalariga ko&lsquo;ra, mehnat unumdorligi va ish soatlari o&lsquo;rtasida bog&lsquo;liqlik mavjudligi aniqlandi &ndash; korrelyatsiya koeffitsiyenti - 0,40. Shunday qilib, O&lsquo;zbekiston sharoitida 4 kunlik ish haftasiga o&lsquo;tish bo&lsquo;yicha jahon amaliyotini iqtisodiyotning barcha tarmoqlarida qo&lsquo;llash maqsadga muvofiq emas. Hisob-kitob natijalariga ko&lsquo;ra, sanoatda ish soatlari va mehnat unumdorligi o&lsquo;rtasidagi korrelyatsiya koeffitsiyenti - 0,45 ni tashkil etdi. Bu yuqori korrelyatsiyani tasdiqlaydi. Buning asosiy sabablari ishlab chiqarishning to&lsquo;liq avtomatlashtirilmaganligi, deb hisoblaymiz.</h3><table border="1" cellpadding="1" cellspacing="1" style="box-sizing: border-box; border-collapse: collapse; border-spacing: 0px; margin: 0px 0px 1.5em; width: 1000px; color: rgb(122, 122, 122); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;"><tbody style="box-sizing: border-box;"><tr style="box-sizing: border-box;"><td style="box-sizing: border-box; padding: 5px; border: 1px solid rgb(221, 221, 221);"><h3 style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 15px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0) !important; font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif; font-weight: 400; font-size: 20px; clear: both; text-align: justify;"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;"><em style="box-sizing: border-box; font-style: italic;">Maʼlumot uchun:</em></strong><em style="box-sizing: border-box; font-style: italic;">&nbsp;<strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">Mehnat unumdorligini hisoblash usuli</strong></em></h3><h3 style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 15px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0) !important; font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif; font-weight: 400; font-size: 20px; clear: both; text-align: justify;"><em style="box-sizing: border-box; font-style: italic;">Mehnat unumdorligi ishlab chiqarilgan mahsulot hajmining (jismoniy yoki pul ko&lsquo;rinishida) ushbu mahsulot hajmini ishlab chiqarishda ishtirok etgan xodimlarning o&lsquo;rtacha soniga nisbati</em></h3><h3 style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 15px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0) !important; font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif; font-weight: 400; font-size: 20px; clear: both; text-align: justify;"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;"><em style="box-sizing: border-box; font-style: italic;">Ish soati uchun mehnat unumdorligini hisoblash:</em></strong></h3><h3 style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 15px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0) !important; font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif; font-weight: 400; font-size: 20px; clear: both; text-align: center;"><em style="box-sizing: border-box; font-style: italic;">MU</em><strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;"><em style="box-sizing: border-box; font-style: italic;">&nbsp;=&nbsp;</em></strong><em style="box-sizing: border-box; font-style: italic;">MH</em><strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;"><em style="box-sizing: border-box; font-style: italic;">&nbsp;/&nbsp;</em></strong><em style="box-sizing: border-box; font-style: italic;">Tsoat</em><strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;"><em style="box-sizing: border-box; font-style: italic;">,</em></strong></h3><h3 style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 15px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0) !important; font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif; font-weight: 400; font-size: 20px; clear: both; text-align: justify;"><em style="box-sizing: border-box; font-style: italic;">bu yerda:</em></h3><h3 style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 15px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0) !important; font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif; font-weight: 400; font-size: 20px; clear: both; text-align: justify;"><em style="box-sizing: border-box; font-style: italic;">MU</em><em style="box-sizing: border-box; font-style: italic;">&nbsp;&ndash; bir ish soati uchun mehnat unumdorligi;</em></h3><h3 style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 15px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0) !important; font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif; font-weight: 400; font-size: 20px; clear: both; text-align: justify;"><em style="box-sizing: border-box; font-style: italic;">MH</em><em style="box-sizing: border-box; font-style: italic;">&nbsp;- ishlab chiqarilgan mahsulot hajmi;</em></h3><h3 style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 15px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0) !important; font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif; font-weight: 400; font-size: 20px; clear: both; text-align: justify;"><em style="box-sizing: border-box; font-style: italic;">Tsoat</em><em style="box-sizing: border-box; font-style: italic;">&nbsp;- maʼlum hajmdagi mahsulot ishlab chiqarish uchun sarflangan ish soatlari soni.</em></h3></td></tr></tbody></table><h3 style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 15px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0) !important; font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif; font-weight: 400; font-size: 20px; clear: both; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; text-align: justify;">Shunga qaramay,&nbsp;<strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">PMTI mutaxassislari</strong> 4 kunlik ish haftasi qo&lsquo;llanilishi mumkin bo&lsquo;lgan sohalarni aniqlashga harakat qildi. Bu nomoddiy ishlab chiqarish sohalari yaʼni, IT sohasi, banklar, taʼlim, sog&lsquo;liqni saqlash, shuningdek, ilm-fan bilan bog&lsquo;liq sohalardir. Shu bilan birga, aytib o&lsquo;tish joizki, IT-sohasidagi xodimlarining aksariyati ancha moslashuvchan ish tartibiga ega. Banklarning 4 kunlik ish haftasiga o&lsquo;tishi moliyaviy operatsiyalarni sekinlashtirishi mumkin. O&lsquo;zbekiston Respublikasi qonunchiligiga muvofiq ishi hissiy, aqliy, asabiy taranglikni kuchaytirish bilan bog&lsquo;liq bo&lsquo;lgan tibbiyot xodimlari va o&lsquo;qituvchilar uchun ish vaqti haftasiga 36 soatdan ko&lsquo;p bo&lsquo;lmagan miqdorda belgilangan (Mehnat kodeksining 118-moddasi). Biroq, tahlil natijalariga ko&lsquo;ra, taʼlim (korrelyatsiya koeffitsenti -0,15), sog&lsquo;liqni saqlash (-0,21), IT-sohasi (-0,09), ilmiy faoliyat (-0,07) va moliya tizimida (-0,06) ish soatlari va mehnat unumdorligi o&lsquo;rtasida korrelyatsion bog&lsquo;liqlik mavjud emas. Bu esa o&lsquo;z navbatida ushbu sohalarda ish vaqtini qisqartirish imkoniyatlari mavjud ekanligidan dalolat beradi.</h3><h3 style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 15px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0) !important; font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif; font-weight: 400; font-size: 20px; clear: both; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; text-align: justify;">Tahlil natijalari mehnat faoliyatining bir yilda qancha davom etishi mehnat unumdorligiga taʼsir qiluvchi yagona va asosiy omil emasligi, ammo ularning o&lsquo;zaro bog&lsquo;liq ekanligi va bunga shubha yo&lsquo;qligini ko&lsquo;rsatdi. Pandemiya sharoitida ko&lsquo;plab korxonalarning o&lsquo;z xodimlarini noilojlikdan masofadan ishlashga o&lsquo;tkazishi ushbu bandlik turi samarali ekanligini ko&lsquo;rsatdi va butun dunyo bo&lsquo;ylab bandlikning turli shakllaridan foydalanish imkonini berdi.</h3><h3 style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 15px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0) !important; font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif; font-weight: 400; font-size: 20px; clear: both; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; text-align: justify;">Yuqoridagi hisob-kitoblar shuni ko&lsquo;rsatadiki, mehnat unumdorligini sifat jihatidan yana-da oshirish va xodimlarning mehnat va dam olish vaqtini uyg&lsquo;unlashtirish nuqtai nazaridan ish haftasini qisqartirish uchun shart-sharoitlar mavjud. Buni bir necha usul bilan amalga oshirish mumkin:</h3><h3 style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 15px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0) !important; font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif; font-weight: 400; font-size: 20px; clear: both; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; text-align: justify;">- to&lsquo;rt kunlik ish haftasiga o&lsquo;tish;</h3><h3 style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 15px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0) !important; font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif; font-weight: 400; font-size: 20px; clear: both; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; text-align: justify;">- xodimlarni qo&lsquo;shimcha &ldquo;o&lsquo;zgaruvchan&rdquo; dam olish kuni bilan taʼminlash;</h3><h3 style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 15px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0) !important; font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif; font-weight: 400; font-size: 20px; clear: both; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; text-align: justify;">- ish vaqtini qisqartirish.</h3><h3 style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 15px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0) !important; font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif; font-weight: 400; font-size: 20px; clear: both; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; text-align: justify;">Moslashuvchan ish jadvaliga o&lsquo;tish va ish haftasini qisqartirish bir qator imtiyozlarni shakllantirishda yordam beradi. Bu esa o&lsquo;z navbatida, umumiy ish samaradorligiga taʼsir qiladi va ijtimoiy-iqtisodiy muhitni yaxshilaydi:</h3><h3 style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 15px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0) !important; font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif; font-weight: 400; font-size: 20px; clear: both; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; text-align: justify;"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">Birinchidan,</strong> xodimlarning sog&lsquo;lig&lsquo;i yaxshilanadi: qo&lsquo;shimcha dam olish kuni xodimlarga yaxshi dam olish va ish uchun kuch to&lsquo;plash imkonini beradi.</h3><h3 style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 15px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0) !important; font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif; font-weight: 400; font-size: 20px; clear: both; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; text-align: justify;"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">Ikkinchidan,</strong> aholining, xususan, xotin-qizlarning mehnat bozoridagi iqtisodiy faolligini oshirish orqali ishsizlikka qarshi samarali kurash taʼminlanadi.</h3><h3 style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 15px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0) !important; font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif; font-weight: 400; font-size: 20px; clear: both; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; text-align: justify;"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">Uchinchidan,</strong> xodimlarning ishtiyoqi kuchayadi, muhim vazifalarni tez va sifatli bajarishda fikrini jamlay oladi, ish vaqtini yo&lsquo;qotish qisqaradi.</h3><h3 style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 15px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0) !important; font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif; font-weight: 400; font-size: 20px; clear: both; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; text-align: justify;"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">To&lsquo;rtinchidan</strong>, ish vaqtini qisqartirish ekologiya va transportga tushadigan zo&lsquo;riqishni, shuningdek, yonilg&lsquo;i va energiya sarfini kamaytirishga ijobiy taʼsir ko&lsquo;rsatadi.</h3><h3 style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 15px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0) !important; font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif; font-weight: 400; font-size: 20px; clear: both; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; text-align: justify;"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">Beshinchidan,</strong> ko&lsquo;ngilochar va madaniyat sohasini rivojlantirishga qo&lsquo;shimcha turtki bo&lsquo;ladi.</h3><h3 style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 15px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0) !important; font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif; font-weight: 400; font-size: 20px; clear: both; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; text-align: justify;"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">Oltinchidan,&nbsp;</strong>aholi turmush darajasi yaxshilanadi. Vaqtni oila davrasida o&lsquo;tkazish, sevimli mashg&lsquo;ulot bilan shug&lsquo;ullanish, madaniy saviyasini yuksaltirish, sport bilan shug&lsquo;ullanish, o&lsquo;z-o&lsquo;zini tarbiyalash uchun keng imkoniyatlar yaratiladi.</h3><h3 style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 15px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0) !important; font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif; font-weight: 400; font-size: 20px; clear: both; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; text-align: justify;">Umuman olganda, xorijiy amaliyotni o&lsquo;rgangan holda, shuningdek, hisob-kitob natijalariga ko&lsquo;ra,&nbsp;<strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">PMTI mutaxassislari</strong> O&lsquo;zbekiston sharoitida ayrim sohalarda 4 kunlik ish haftasiga o&lsquo;tish imkoniyatlari mavjud, deb hisoblaydi.</h3><h3 style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 15px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0) !important; font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif; font-weight: 400; font-size: 20px; clear: both; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; text-align: justify;"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">&nbsp;</strong></h3><h3 style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 15px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0) !important; font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif; font-weight: 400; font-size: 20px; clear: both; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; text-align: justify;"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">M.Ahmedova,<br style="box-sizing: border-box;">PMTI guruh rahbari</strong></h3></header><div style="box-sizing: inherit; color: rgb(114, 114, 114); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;"><div style="box-sizing: inherit; margin: 0px;"><div data-elementor-type="wp-post" data-elementor-id="4823" data-elementor-settings="[]" style="box-sizing: inherit; hyphens: manual;"><div style="box-sizing: border-box;"><div style="box-sizing: border-box;"><section data-id="3a4a538" data-element_type="section" style="box-sizing: border-box; display: block; position: relative;"><div style="box-sizing: border-box; display: flex; margin-right: auto; margin-left: auto; position: relative; max-width: 100%;"><div style="box-sizing: border-box; width: 1160px; display: flex;"><div data-id="b12e115" data-element_type="column" style="box-sizing: border-box; position: relative; min-height: 1px; display: flex; width: 1160px;"><div style="box-sizing: border-box; width: 1160px; position: relative; display: flex; padding: 0px 10px 10px;"><div style="box-sizing: border-box; position: relative; width: 1140px; flex-wrap: wrap; align-content: flex-start; display: flex;"><div data-id="7c752be" data-element_type="widget" data-widget_type="text-editor.default" style="box-sizing: border-box; position: relative; color: rgb(122, 122, 122); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-weight: 400; width: 1140px;"><div style="box-sizing: border-box; transition: background 0.3s ease 0s, border 0.3s ease 0s, border-radius 0.3s ease 0s, box-shadow 0.3s ease 0s, -webkit-border-radius 0.3s ease 0s, -webkit-box-shadow 0.3s ease 0s;"><div style="box-sizing: border-box;"><br></div><